summary: A small mod that changes the mesh and Retextures Spellbreaker!
descriptionHtml:
[center][color=#674ea7][size=3]A small mod that changes the mesh and Retextures Spellbreaker!

Meshes from [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/33922/?]Ifterich's Spellbreaker Remesh[/url]
Textures from [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/58015/?]zzjay's Oblivionized Spellbreaker[/url]
Thanks to both zzjay and Ifterich for giving me permission to use their assets so go and give them both Endorsements they Deserve it!
